text: Mair Eluned Morgan, Baroness Morgan of Ely (born 16 February 1967) is a Welsh Labour politician who is currently serving as the First Minister of Wales and the Leader of Welsh Labour since 2024. She previously served as Cabinet Secretary for Health and Social Care in the Welsh Government from 2021 to 2024. ==Notes== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Heads of government Category:Members of the Senedd Category:First Ministers of Wales Category:Politicians from Cardiff Category:Labour Party (UK) people Category:MEPs for the United Kingdom ==References==
